text: Multan District () is a district in the Punjab province of Pakistan. According to the 1998 census of Pakistan it had a population of 3.117 million (1.315 million or 42.2% in urban areas). Its capital is the city of Multan. == Tehsils of Multan == * Mumtazabad Tehsil * Sher Shah Tehsil * Sujaabad Tehsil * Jalapur Pirwala Tehsil * Bosan Tehsil * Shah Rukn-e-alam Tehsil ==References== Category:Districts of British India Category:Multan Division
